OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMore head teachers quitting
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwithin five years of taking
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fjobs in England            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of head teachers in England 
OL,6, quitting their jobs within the first   
OL,7, five years of starting is on the rise. 
OL,9,FOne in four (25%) primary school heads 
OL,10,Fand more than one in three (37%) in    
OL,11,Fsecondary schools who started their    
OL,12,Froles in 2015 had left by 2020 - up    
OL,13,Ffrom 21% and 35% since 2011.           
OL,15,F"Crushing workloads" and frozen pay    
OL,16,Fwere to blame, said the NAHT union.    
OL,18,FThe government said that while school  
OL,19,Fleaders have faced challenges, the     
OL,20,Foverall picture is positive.           
